                <note rend="inline" type="source">814.00/1044: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in Guatemala</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Whitehouse</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Guatemala</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1931-01-05T17:00:00-07:00"
                            >January 5, 1931—5 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/>[Received 8:55 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>7. The decree calling elections for President to take place on February 6th, 7th
                    and 8th was issued on January 3rd.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Whitehouse</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
